Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&3A4B71\4c&3A4B71}嗯 早啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&3A4B71\4c&3A4B71}她这回归平常的状态了 还挺让我惊讶的
